{"tid":1745341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［Org Chem撚入］究竟點解有氯就會有二噁英？","createTime":"2019-11-22T07:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:20:54.000Z","uid":44924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c478f4004c6e3987780326a57a80f4c8763e1795","tid":1745341,"uid":44924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:16:22.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到隔離牛河博士個post，就去左search下二噁英既構成條件，發覺原來只要organic野入面有chlorine再加熱，就會出二噁英。<br />\n<br />\n作為一個org chem撚，當然要諗埋個mechanism先得啦，利申：以下全部鳩估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx</span><br />\n<br />\n首先chlorine要變oxygen，本身都唔係一件易既事，Cl 本身係electrophile，而O2本身亦唔係nucleophile<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以傳統既nucleophilic substitution就肯定唔work架啦。<br />\n<br />\n所以，我唯一諗到既可能就係radical substitution。點解咁講呢，係因為本身O2本身就係一個diradical，而Cl本身都係一個好既leaving group 。本身O2要去substitute左Cl就係endothermic同reversible既，不過係高溫既情況底下要做到呢樣野唔難。<br />\n<br />\n咁係substitute左既-C-O-O&middot; 之後又會點呢？O-O bond本身係易斷既，所以個O既radical可以take up兩個H&middot;變左水咁甩出黎，呢個都係好common既radical reaction入面見到既。而最尾呢就會出到-C-O&middot;既structure，之後既chain reaction就好難predict啦，但大致上二噁英既基本structure已經有。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx</span><br />\n<br />\nRadical reaction最緊要係睇Bond Dissociation Energy（BDE），假設我既推論正確，我想問下RSC院士牛河博士，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">C-H bond既BDE係幾多呀，C-Cl bond既BDE又係幾多呀，O2可唔可以做Hydrogen Atom Transfer呀，普通燒膠可以出到二噁英，你啲thermodynamics係唔係白讀架屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n以上皆是鳩估，求各位高手指正。"},{"pid":"e17ed5221b1bec55e612cee1584a247eb77d8577","tid":1745341,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"第一句<br />\n首先chlorine要變oxygen<br />\n<br />\n好心你寫清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熟chem嘅人會估到你講乜，但係大眾會覺得你係煉金術師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b442117ad47e85ed81e84e55a8899b54f8429d","tid":1745341,"uid":44924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e17ed5221b1bec55e612cee1584a247eb77d8577","tid":1745341,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"第一句<br />\n首先chlorine要變oxygen<br />\n<br />\n好心你寫清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 熟chem嘅人會估到你講乜，但係大眾會覺得你係煉金術師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:23:14.000Z","msg":"Sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打得太快冇proofread 到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nChem撚明就得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ee8a6c94bd3196f108ce5b2352649944d19df4","tid":1745341,"uid":44924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:33:36.000Z","msg":"推到Org chem高手見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2083e856038a2833e600d4d8f3f963a4dfb8f7be","tid":1745341,"uid":44924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"5eb25a5e66d2d1d118e7e7693d3d795031f7a9a5","tid":1745341,"uid":44924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c088c6f459a3ce748b81c34466e21b0fa5c44b64","tid":1745341,"uid":81156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"92b442117ad47e85ed81e84e55a8899b54f8429d","tid":1745341,"uid":44924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e17ed5221b1bec55e612cee1584a247eb77d8577","tid":1745341,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:19:52.000Z","msg":"第一句<br />\n首先chlorine要變oxygen<br />\n<br />\n好心你寫清楚啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif